      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition example that presents beautifully throughout and appears to have been very well kept. The paint, trim, glass, and brightwork show extremely well, the interior is clean and highly detailed, and the car has the kind of fit, finish, and overall freshness buyers hope to find but rarely do. It appears complete, properly sorted, and ready to enjoy immediately, whether for local shows, weekend drives, or adding to a collection. For a buyer, this is the kind of car that stands out for its presentation and care, with very little to nitpick compared with the average driver-quality example.",
